			<p><strong>The Privacy Policy</strong></p>

<p>This Privacy Policy ("Privacy Policy") applies to Passport Services LLC, its parents and related entities, subsidiaries, whether or not wholly owned ("Passport Services LLC") and specifically, it outlines the types of information that Passport Services LLC gathers about you ("User") while you are using the https://www.passportservicesllc.com website or any other website that links to or uses the Passport Services LLC Service now or in the future ("Passport Services LLC Website(s)"). This Privacy Policy is incorporated into and is subject to thePassport Services LLC Terms of Use. Your use of the Passport Services LLC Website and any personal information you provide on the Passport Services LLC Website remains subject to the terms of this Privacy Policy and our Terms of Use. </p>
